  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Season the trout fillets with salt and black pepper.",
    "In a bowl, mix olive oil, dill, garlic powder, Herbes de Provence, ground flaxseed, and coconut flour. Mix well until crumbly.",
